@startuml svc-check-in--post-check-ins

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #059669
    ParticipantBorderColor #2E86AB
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F4F8
    LifeLineBorderColor #A23B72
    BoxBorderColor #F18F01
    BoxBackgroundColor #FFF8F0
    NoteBorderColor #c77b30
    NoteBackgroundColor #FEF3E7
}

header [[/microservices/svc-check-in/#integration-context ⬆ svc-check-in Integration Context]]

title POST /check-ins\nInitiate check-in for a participant\n<size:10><color:#7c3aed>ARCHITECT OVERRIDE — enriched with internal behavior</color></size>

participant "Client" as Client [[/applications/]]
participant "API Gateway" as GW [[/actors/#api-gateway]] #DBEAFE
participant "svc-check-in" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-check-in/]] #E8F4F8
participant "Reservations" as Res [[/microservices/svc-reservations/]] #FFF8F0
participant "Guest Profiles" as GP [[/microservices/svc-guest-profiles/]] #FFF8F0
participant "Trip Catalog" as TC [[/microservices/svc-trip-catalog/]] #FFF8F0
participant "Safety Compliance" as Safety [[/microservices/svc-safety-compliance/]] #FFF8F0
participant "Notifications" as Ntfy [[/microservices/svc-notifications/]] #FFF8F0
database "Redis" as Cache #FFE0B2
database "PostgreSQL" as DB [[/microservices/svc-check-in/#data-store]] #FCE4EC

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-check-in.html#/Check-Ins/createCheckIn View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> GW : POST /check-ins
activate GW #059669
GW -> Svc : route request
activate Svc #059669

note right of Svc : Validate request body\n(reservation_id, guest_id required)

== Reservation Validation ==

Svc -> Res : [[/microservices/svc-reservations/#get-reservationsreservation_id-get-reservation-details GET /reservations/{id}]]
activate Res #DBEAFE
Res --> Svc : Reservation details\n(adventure_category, trip_id, status)
deactivate Res
note right of Svc : Reject if status != CONFIRMED

== Guest Identity — Session Cache ==

Svc -> Cache : GET session:{kiosk_token}:{guest_id}
activate Cache #FFE0B2
alt Cache HIT
    Cache --> Svc : Cached guest profile
    deactivate Cache
else Cache MISS
    Cache --> Svc : null
    deactivate Cache
    Svc -> GP : [[/microservices/svc-guest-profiles/#get-guestsguest_id-get-guest-profile GET /guests/{guest_id}]]
    activate GP #DBEAFE
    GP --> Svc : Guest profile
    deactivate GP
    Svc -> Cache : SET session:{kiosk_token}:{guest_id}\nTTL 15 min (ADR-009)
    activate Cache #FFE0B2
    Cache --> Svc : OK
    deactivate Cache
end

== Adventure Classification (ADR-004, ADR-005) ==

Svc -> TC : [[/microservices/svc-trip-catalog/#get-tripstrip_id-get-trip-details GET /trips/{trip_id}]]
activate TC #DBEAFE
TC --> Svc : Trip details\n(adventure_category)
deactivate TC

note right of Svc : Map adventure_category\nto check-in pattern\nvia configuration (ADR-004)\n\nUnknown categories\ndefault to Pattern 3 (ADR-005)

alt Pattern 2 or Pattern 3 (guided/full service)
    == Waiver Validation ==
    Svc -> Safety : [[/microservices/svc-safety-compliance/#get-waivers-list-waivers-by-guest GET /waivers?guest_id={guest_id}]]
    activate Safety #DBEAFE
    Safety --> Svc : Active waivers
    deactivate Safety
    note right of Svc : Reject if no valid\nwaiver on file
else Pattern 1 (basic self-check-in)
    note right of Svc : Waiver check skipped\n(low-risk adventure)
end

== Database Transaction ==

group Transaction boundary (PostgreSQL)
    Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO check_ins\n(check_in_id, reservation_id,\nguest_id, adventure_category,\ncheck_in_pattern, status)
    activate DB #FCE4EC
    DB --> Svc : Created row
    deactivate DB

    Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO wristband_assignments\n(wristband_id, check_in_id,\nrfid_tag, assigned_at)
    activate DB #FCE4EC
    DB --> Svc : Created row
    deactivate DB
end

== Async Events ==

Svc ->> Ntfy : [[/microservices/svc-notifications/#post-notifications-send-a-notification Send check-in confirmation]]

Svc --> GW : 201 Created\n(check_in_id, wristband_id,\ncheck_in_pattern)
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 201 Created
deactivate GW

@enduml
